      <p class="eyebrow">Coming soon</p>
      <h1>The Waking</h1>
      <p class="lede">One story, told as three books. A girl crosses out of a grief-struck life into a world with its own currency, its own wars, and its own way home. She survives it twice. The third crossing is the one that matters.</p>
      <p class="strapline">Everything she loves is in one world. Everyone who loves her is in the other.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="how-pull">
    <div class="wrap">
      <p class="big">Something beneath the world is bleeding through.</p>
      <p>Read them close. The light is always where she needs it. A voice keeps almost reaching her. A patient tone under everything keeps a count no one will explain. Every answer waits at the end of Book&nbsp;3, and it is worth the wait.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="how-section">
