        <div class="role">
          <h3><a href="/books/beyond-the-pale/">I. Beyond the Pale</a></h3>
          <p>A boundary crossed. A world found, with marbles for money and a war she never chose. The way out is the way in, run backwards.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="role">
          <h3><a href="/books/paupers-weatherglass/">II. Pauper's Weatherglass</a></h3>
          <p>The barometer of a coming storm. The flower closes before the rain, and the rain is coming for everything.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="role">
          <h3><a href="/books/the-persistence-of-memory/">III. The Persistence of Memory</a></h3>
          <p>What survives the crossing. The climb, the deep, and what it costs to come all the way home.</p>
